									  Meet the Team					  
Meet the Team



Focus on What Is Most Important to You
We simplify the complexity that exists where family and wealth intersect
Bringing exceptional people, technology, and process together, our integrated planning and implementation has helped families become stronger, grow their investments, and build their legacies.
Each member of your multi-disciplinary, multi-generational Pitcairn team, as well as our firm’s leadership will be proactive with our interaction and communication with you. You will also benefit from access to our global network of clients, intermediaries, and talented professionals—an exclusive set of trusted contacts and valuable resources.
Please click on a team member's name below to view their personal biography:
 



