Catherine Rooney - Pitcairn Trust Company - The Wall Street Transcript














































 






































General Investing >> Money Manager Interviews >> September 23, 2002 Catherine Rooney – Pitcairn Trust Company
CATHERINE E. ROONEY is Vice President and Portfolio Manager at
Pitcairn Trust Company, responsible for portfolio management of
the Select Value and Diversified Value Strategies and Socially
Responsive Investing portfolios as well as for equity investment
decisions within the following sectors: pharmaceuticals,
restaurant, retail, food and beverage, and technology. Prior to
joining Pitcairn, she was Vice President and Director of Research
of Merus Capital Management, a Security Analyst at Wilmington
Trust and a Security Analyst at Josephthal & Company. She
received her MBA and BBA degrees from Temple University and is a
Chartered Financial Analyst. Profile


